In compliance with the applicable MCA circulars and SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulation 2015 Please find enclosed herewith the copies of the Newspaper advertisement of the public notice to the shareholders published on 21st August 2025 intimating that the 35th AGM of the company will be held on 12.09.2025 in the following newspapers;
1. Financial Express (English) and          
2. Mumbai Lakshdeep (Marathi)
